OL,4,CCovid-19: New rules for schools in
OL,5,CEngland to be set out
OL,6, England's schools will find out later
OL,7, how the government plans to relax rules
OL,8, that have led to large numbers of
OL,9, pupils being sent home if a single
OL,10, child has a positive Covid test.
OL,12,FLast week the "bubble" system saw more
OL,13,Fthan 375,000 children sent home.
OL,15,FIt has meant missed days of lessons for
OL,16,Fthousands of pupils and frustration for
OL,17,Fparents juggling work and childcare.
OL,19,FThe announcement will come amid a
OL,20,Fbacklash to government plans to ditch
OL,21,Frules on the wearing of face masks.
